OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing in places this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight, with the odd clear and
OL,8,Fdrier spell. Milder than previous
OL,9,Fnight with most places staying above
OL,10,Ffreezing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAnother mixed day with
OL,13,Fshowers, these heavy at times and most
OL,14,Ffrequent in the south during the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Drier in Cumbria later with
OL,16,Fsunny spells. Feeling slightly warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
