OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry in
OL,6,Fthe west on Saturday but rain over the
OL,7,Fhills in the east. Drier and brighter
OL,8,Fon Sunday but breezier. Cloudy again
OL,9,Fon Monday with rain. Turning cooler.
